title: Tristan Rennie's Transitional Conquest for Santa Cruz Skateboards
description:
Congrats on your 5th Place finish at the Vans Pool Party, Tristan! 
Drain some pools and fire up the Makita with Santa Cruz AM Tristan Rennie!...The dude's been stacking some heavy clips and keeping the backyard pool torch lit. Enjoy..
